These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  architect, designer, pilot, firefighter, software-developer, librarian, coach
There are 7 different nationalities: french, turkish, polish, indonesian, indian, russian, dutch
 1. the firefighter is on the left of the indonesian##1
 2. the indian is the firefighter##1
 3. the coach is on the right of the librarian##1
 4. the polish is on the right of the russian##1
 5. the pilot is in the middle##1
 6. the french is on the far left##1
 7. the software-developer is the french##1
 8. the architect is on the right of the russian##1
 9. the polish is on the left of the turkish##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the pilot##1
11. the coach is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | software-developer | firefighter | designer | pilot | architect | librarian | coach |
| Nationality   | french    | indian   | indonesian      | russian | polish    | turkish    | dutch         |

