.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: broccoli, carrot, potato, avocado, lettuce, artichoke, pomegranate
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, reggae, salsa, indie, dubstep, classical, blues
 1. the fan of dubstep is the person eating avocado##1
 2. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 3. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 5. the person eating avocado is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 6. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 7. the fan of dubstep is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 9. the fan of blues is on the left of the person eating potato##1
10. the person eating avocado is on the left of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | broccoli | carrot | lettuce | avocado | artichoke | pomegranate | potato |
| Music-Genre   | reggae      | salsa   | indie   | dubstep      | electronic       | blues       | classical     |

