.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: grapefruit, tomato, peas, carrot, kiwi, broccoli, banana
The people have 7 different jobs:  librarian, musician, accountant, fisherman, doctor, chef, security-guard
 1. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 2. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the security-guard##1
 3. the musician is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 4. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 5. the librarian is the person eating kiwi##1
 6. the accountant is on the right of the musician##1
 7. the musician is on the left of the accountant##1
 8. the musician is on the right of the fisherman##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is the fisherman##1
10. the person eating peas is on the right of the librarian##1
11. the fisherman is in the middle##1
12. the person eating banana is on the left of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | tomato | kiwi     | peas  | broccoli       | grapefruit       | banana  | carrot   |
| Job    | chef  | librarian | security-guard | fisherman | musician | accountant | doctor |

