.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, gospel, punk, country, dubstep, blues, funk
There are 7 different nationalities: british, russian, german, dutch, italian, canadian, polish
 1. the fan of dubstep is the russian##1
 2. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 3. the canadian is on the right of the german##1
 4. the british is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 5. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 6. the fan of blues is on the far left##1
 7. the german is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the right of the canadian##1
 9. the fan of punk is the italian##1
10. the italian is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
11. the polish is the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | blues    | funk     | country     | punk      | gospel | dubstep      | hip-hop     |
| Nationality   | dutch | german | canadian | italian | polish | russian | british |

