.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: rock-climbing, photography, card-games, collecting, filmmaking, camping, singing
7 different pets are kept: turtle, goat, cat, ferret, bird, mouse, chinchilla
 1. the person who's hobby is photography is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | photography | card-games | camping     | collecting | singing | filmmaking | rock-climbing |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | cat    | bird | mouse     | turtle         | ferret     | goat        |

