.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, tea, water, milk, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, scooter, car, subway, motorbike, bike, snowmobile
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the taxi##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | tea | fanta   | lemonade | water | hot-chocolate  | milk | mirinda |
| Transport   | subway   | motorbike | taxi | bike     | scooter | snowmobile | car   |

