 3. the person watching western movies is the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person driving the van is the person watching comedy movies##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
10. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | western | documentary | sports | family     | disaster | comedy |
| Transport     | subway | tram      | bike | helicopter    | taxi | train   | van  |

