 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 8. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
